definitions.definition: A village and civil parish in South Cambridgeshire district, Cambridgeshire , England ( OS grid ref TL3770 ) .

A hamlet in Almondsbury parish, South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire , England ( OS grid ref ST5882 )
